description: Boston Facts is to help everyone learn more about the city of Boston in Massachusetts in the United States. For diehard Bostonians to future visitors, learn more about the great city of Boston! Get started by asking Boston Facts for a Boston fact and you'll get a random fact about the city of Boston. No accounts are needed to get started.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Boston Facts for a Boston fact
Alexa, ask boston facts to tell me a boston trivia
Alexa, ask boston facts to give me some boston information
name: Boston Facts
shortDescription: Boston Facts will tell you wondrous, glorious facts about the City of Boston! Use "Alexa, ask Boston Facts for a Boston Fact".
